        frequency by <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">students</ENAMEX> if the instruction had been
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">integrated</ENAMEX> across all the clerkships and linked to
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">students</ENAMEX>' clinical duties. However, even with course
        improvements, we might have achieved success in teaching a
