        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">students</ENAMEX> will have when they enter practice.
        Further research and development of more efficient
        strategies for seeking medical evidence are needed. Haynes
        recently questioned, "Is it time to change how you seek
        best evidence" and proposed that we first seek evidence in
