        strategy is to search a systematic textbook <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</NUMEX>, and then
        use an automated meta-search engine to seek evidence
        published since the literature search of the systematic
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">textbook</ENAMEX>. However, research is needed to assess the
